        SHORT="bmon is an interface bandwidth monitor."

cat << EOF
bmon is an interface bandwidth monitor.

It is able to generate and draw three types of diagrams:
* The overview diagram which is a list of all interfaces and their send/receive rates.
* A very MRTG like graphical diagram in ASCII showing the rate over a specific time period in a bar diagram.
* The details diagram which contains all counters of an interface such as total bytes sent/received, errors, compressed packets, ...
EOF
